data.description: An unbeatable location - just steps from Lake Holiday, in the Indian Hills subdivision! This home offers the space & comfort you are looking for - both inside and out. On just under an acre of land, this home features 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths and over 2000sqft. of living space! Open concept & spacious interior with large kitchen & lots of storage. Cozy den/family room space with wood burning fireplace. Formal dining room, as well as a formal living room space. Step outside to a giant deck - perfect for entertaining! Beautiful outdoor space, with a small fenced-in yard on the side and an enormous front yard. 2-car detached garage offers more storage space! Indian Hills has so much to offer! Move in, and enjoy the private lake! Inspections welcome but being sold as AS IS.
